props.name: initialValue
props.description: The initial value for the form field.

props.name: validateOnValueUpdate
props.description: Whether to validate the form field when the value change.

props.name: validateOnBlur
props.description: Whether to validate the form field when it loses focus (on blur).

props.name: validateOnMount
props.description: Whether to validate the form field immediately after the form is mounted.

props.name: validateOnSubmit
props.description: Whether to validate the form field when the form is submitted.

props.name: as
props.type: string | Component<any, any, any, ComputedOptions, MethodOptions, Object, any>
props.description: Use to change the HTML tag of root element.

props.name: asChild
props.description: When enabled, it changes the default rendered element for the one passed as a child element.

props.name: dt
props.description: It generates scoped CSS variables using design tokens for the component.

props.name: pt
props.description: Used to pass attributes to DOM elements inside the component.

props.name: ptOptions
props.description: Used to configure passthrough(pt) options of the component.

props.name: unstyled
props.description: When enabled, it removes component related styles in the core.
